        ============
        ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
        Look up and report on the DMARC status of a domain
        ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
        
        :Author: `Michael JasonSmith`_
        :Contact: Michael JasonSmith <mpj17@onlinegroups.net>
        :Date: 2014-09-29
        :Organization: `GroupServer.org`_
        :Copyright: This document is licensed under a
